description.narrative: The project development objectives (PDO) are: (i) for the Doukkala ORMVA, the Gharb ORMVA, the Haouz ORMVA and the Tadla ORMVA, to provide an improved water service to farmers, and (ii) for targeted farmers in the Project Area, to have better access to improved irrigation technologies.
